description: This hall of fame Cooter purrs with a rating of 94, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 282, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 1 for East, 1 for South, and 1 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [282 Votes, Hall of Fame]
